c: 10
v: 104
t: "Yithi (Muhammad): “Hini na bantu! Ukuba nineentandabuzo mayela neNkolo yam [i-Islam, (kwazini kakuhle)] ke okokuba mna andisokuze ndizinqule ezo zinto nizinqulayo nina ngaphandle koAllâh, kodwa mna ndiya kunqula uAllah ekunguYe Onenza nife, yaye mna ndiyalelwe ukuba ndibe ngomnye wamakholwa"